Summarize Data Availability

dr_getoverview.Rd

Retrieve a table of available DATRAS survey-year-quarter combinations. This function is a wrapper around icesDatras::getDatrasDataOverview, returning a tibble rather than a list of matrices.

Usage

dr_getoverview(surveys = NULL)

Arguments

surveys

A character vector of survey names to process, or NULL to process all surveys.

Value

A tibble with columns survey, year, and quarter for available data.
